Connecting to HPC:
    ssh s244804@login1.gbar.dtu.dk

To choose a node of GPU's check the link
    https://www.hpc.dtu.dk/?page_id=2129#LSF

Use the following command to send a file to the HCP (in PowerShell)
    scp "folder_path" ` s244804@transfer.gbar.dtu.dk:~/TestRepo/Data

Use the following command to send a folder to the HCP (in PowerShell)
    scp -r "folder_path" ` s244804@transfer.gbar.dtu.dk:~/TestRepo/Data
    scp -r s244804@transfer.gbar.dtu.dk:~/TestRepo/Data ' "C:/Users/kaspe/Desktop/DTU/4. Semester/Project Work/HPCLocal"

Use the following command to check available devices
    nvidia-smi

Use the following command to choose available device
    CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES= available_device, python_script.py

    CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=1 python TestHPC.py